SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, Line 12c
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: ANNUALLY, THE INTERNATIONAL AGRI-CENTER BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND EX-OFFICIO DIRECTORS SIGN A CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY. THE DIRECTORS ARE REQUIRED TO DISCLOSE ANY CONFLICT OF INTEREST AND NOT PARTICIPATE IN THE BOARD MEETING FOR THE ENTIRE TIME THE MATTER IS DISCUSSED AND VOTED UPON.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, Line 15b
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HAS THEIR PERSONNEL COMMITTEE EVALUATE AND MAKE RECOMMENDATIONS REGARDING COMPENSATION WHICH ARE THEN EITHER APPROVED, MODIFIED OR DENIED BY THE ENTIRE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section C, Line 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: CONDENSED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS ARE PUBLISHED IN THE ORGANIZATION NEWSLETTER. COMPLETE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND OTHER GOVERNING DOCUMENTS ARE MADE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST IN THE ORGANIZATIONS CORPORATE OFFICE.OUR ANNUAL REPORT IS ON OUR WEBSITE.
